          "$x = -2$",
          "$x = 5$",
          "$x = -5$"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "Expand: $f(x) = x^2 - 4x - 21$. $x = \\frac{4}{2} = 2$. Axis: $x = 2$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "A company's profit is $P(x) = -5x^2 + 150x - 1000$, where $x$ is items sold. What is the maximum profit?",
        "options": [
          "$100",
          "$125",
          "$150",
          "$225"
        ],
        "answer": "B",
        "explanation": "$x = \\frac{-150}{2(-5)} = 15$. $P(15) = -5(225) + 150(15) - 1000 = -1125 + 2250 - 1000 = 125$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "What are the x-intercepts of $f(x) = 2x^2 + 11x - 21$?",
        "options": [
          "$x = \\frac{3}{2}$ and $x = -7$",
          "$x = -\\frac{3}{2}$ and $x = 7$",
          "$x = 3$ and $x = -\\frac{7}{2}$",
          "$x = \\frac{7}{2}$ and $x = -3$"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$x = \\frac{-11 \\pm \\sqrt{121 + 168}}{4} = \\frac{-11 \\pm 17}{4}$. $x = \\frac{3}{2}$, $x = -7$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "A rectangle has an area of 72 square feet. The length is 6 feet more than the width. What is the width?",
        "options": [
          "6 feet",
          "8 feet",
          "12 feet",
          "4 feet"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$w(w + 6) = 72 \\rightarrow w^2 + 6w - 72 = 0 \\rightarrow (w + 12)(w - 6) = 0$. $w = 6$ feet."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Find the y-coordinate of the vertex of $f(x) = \\frac{2}{3}x^2 - 4x + 9$.",
        "options": [
          "3",
          "6",
          "9",
          "12"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$x = \\frac{4}{2(2/3)} = \\frac{4}{4/3} = 3$. $f(3) = \\frac{2}{3}(9) - 12 + 9 = 6 - 12 + 9 = 3$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "The product of two consecutive even integers is 48. Find the smaller integer.",
        "options": [
          "4",
          "6",
          "8",
          "12"
        ],
        "answer": "B",
        "explanation": "$x(x + 2) = 48 \\rightarrow x^2 + 2x - 48 = 0 \\rightarrow (x + 8)(x - 6) = 0$. $x = 6$."
      }
